**John Paul II**

**Bishop of Rome**
John Paul in 1988

**Church** [Catholic Church](/Catholic_Church)
**Papacy began** 16 October 1978
**Papacy ended** 2 April 2005
**Predecessor** [John Paul I](/John_Paul_I)
**Successor** [Benedict XVI](/Benedict_XVI)

**Previous posts**
* [Titular Bishop](/Titular_Bishop) of [Ombi](/Kom_Ombo) (1958–1964)
